(1561, '7-23D6', 'E7', 'D', 23, 'Which of the following statements concerning MMSI is true?', 'All ship station MMSI must begin with a single zero and include the MID.', 'All group station MMSI must begin with the MID.', 'None of these answers are correct.', 'All Coast Station MMSI must be 9 digits and begin with the MID and then two zeros.', 'C', 0),
