(1654, '7-39F3', 'E7', 'F', 39, 'How can a SART''s detection and effective range be maximized?', 'The SART should be held or mounted as high as possible and in a vertical position.', 'The SART should be placed in water immediately so it will begin transmitting.', 'Switch the SART into the "high" power position.', 'If possible, the SART should be mounted horizontally so that its signal matches that of the searching radar signal.', 'A', 0),
