(1656, '7-39F5', 'E7', 'F', 39, 'At what point does a SART begin transmitting?', 'It immediately begins radiating when placed in the "on" position.', 'If it has been placed in the "on" position, it will respond when it has been interrogated by a 9-GHz radar signal.', 'It must be manually activated or water activated before radiating.', 'If it has been placed in the "on" position, it will begin transmitting immediately upon detecting that it is in water.', 'B', 0),
