(2979, '9-10A2', 'E9', 'A', 10, '?Which of the following best describes a VHF collinear array?', 'An antenna with phased elements, omni directional radiation pattern, offering up to 9 db gain.', 'The cascade filters in the VHF radio''s IF section.', '?A shoreside directional VHF yagi antenna.', 'A depth sounder phased array transducer.', 'A', 0),
(2980, '9-10A3', 'E9', 'A', 10, 'A masthead antenna with a base loading coil appears shorted to an ohmmeter check.?What might this indicate?', 'Positive proof of shorted coaxial cable plugs.', 'May be normal for a well working shunt fed?antenna system.', 'Immediately repair both upper and lower?PL-259s.', 'No VHF antenna should measure a short circuit.??', 'B', 0),
